%% Sequence Diagram — End-to-End RAG Query Flow

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant QP as Query Processor
    participant Ret as Hybrid Retriever
    participant Qdrant
    participant RR as Re-ranker
    participant CB as Context Builder
    participant PM as Prompt Manager
    participant LLM as LLM Orchestration
    participant OAI as OpenAI
    participant PG as PostgreSQL

    User->>API: POST /query {question, filters}
    API->>QP: Normalize & validate query
    QP->>Ret: Build retrieval request + metadata filters

    Ret->>Qdrant: Dense vector search (top-k)
    Ret->>Qdrant: Keyword / payload filter search
    Qdrant-->>Ret: Candidate chunks (merged)

    Ret->>RR: Re-rank candidates by relevance
    RR-->>CB: Top-N ranked chunks

    CB->>CB: Assemble grounded context window
    CB->>PM: Context + user question
    PM->>PM: Apply system prompt template
    PM->>LLM: Grounded prompt payload

    LLM->>OAI: Chat completion request
    OAI-->>LLM: Generated response + token usage
    LLM-->>API: Grounded answer + citations

    API->>PG: Log query, latency, cost, chunk IDs
    API-->>User: Response with sources & metadata
